      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Rocket Launch Tracker\n\nA fun showcase using publicly-inspired space launch data to demonstrate Infinity's inline JSON mode and DataTable's value mapping + external clickthrough features.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- \ud83d\ude80 **Infinity datasource** \u2014 data embedded inline, no API calls\n- \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f **Value mappings** \u2014 1 \u2192 Nominal, 2 \u2192 Anomaly, 0 \u2192 Abort, 3 \u2192 Scrubbed\n- \ud83d\udd17 **Clickthrough** \u2014 click an org name in the preview to open the full table; on the full table, org names link to their external website\n- \ud83d\udd0d **Search** \u2014 type to find any rocket, org, or payload\n\n[Open Full Launches Table \u2192](/d/dt-space-launches)",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        }
      }
    },
